name: High_Low_Bot
description:
This game is a simple "Guess Your Number" where you think of a number between 1 and 1000 and the computer, known as the "High_Low_Bot", will hack and gain access to your brain obtaining the correct guess!

This project is for Section 4 of the Udemy Course "Complete C# Unity Developer 2D: Learn to Code Making Games" by Gamedev.tv. The course can be found at https://www.udemy.com/course/unitycourse/.

Note: The current game may contain bugs or be incomplete due to being a tutorial project, however this might be updated in the future!
